						               													<description>Track Design to the Finish Line!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Mad Rush Rally is a game where you take turns building the track while you're racing on it! This allows you to create the track to suit your own strategy. You can even design your own short-cut to jump to first place!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players gain insane and fun-to-use items; Items like the Booster, which let's you jet ahead of the competition; the Dodge Ball, which whacks your friend into missing their next turn; the Squirrel, which creates a roadblock forcing players to change course; or the Bomb which decimates the track and all on it! Plus more items that shift the balance of the game! What's more, some items are left on the track to be used by or to hinder your friends, making each game even more unique.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Mad Rush Rally offers a familiar but fresh experience combining kart racing inspired video games with a simple yet revolutionary map-building game mechanic that brings fun back to the table.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
